    "article": "Article II. THE CREDITS",
    "section": "Section 2.03",
    "title": "Requests for Borrowings",
    "url": "docs/doc4-credit-agreement.html#sec-2-03",
    "summary": "Requests for Borrowings. Borrowing requests must be submitted to the Administrative Agent with specified notice periods: 3 business days for SOFR borrowings, same day for ABR borrowings. Each request is irrevocable and must specify the class,...",
