    "content": "Covenants for the Exchangeable Notes include standard high-yield restrictions plus additional structural covenants unique to the Muvico Group entity structure. Key additions include: corporate separateness requirements (Sec 4.20) to maintain Muvico as a distinct entity, intercompany agreement restrictions (Sec 4.21), and controls on amendments to key documents (Sec 4.22). These structural covenants protect the ring-fenced Muvico asset base."
